Kkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼv">&lt;video</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">width</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"400"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">controls</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;source</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">src</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"video.mp4"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">type</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"video/mp4"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>  Ваш браузер не поддерживает видео</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/video&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="262" data-end="265">
<h1 data-section-id="183zspf" data-start="267" data-end="286">🔥 ЧТО ЭТО ЗНАЧИТ</h1>
<ul data-start="288" data-end="459">
<li data-section-id="179gd3d" data-start="288" data-end="325">
<p data-start="290" data-end="325"><code data-start="290" data-end="297">video</code> → вставляет видео на сайт</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1m7xfu2" data-start="326" data-end="368">
<p data-start="328" data-end="368"><code data-start="328" data-end="341">width="400"</code> → размер (можешь менять)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12ofhln" data-start="369" data-end="412">
<p data-start="371" data-end="412"><code data-start="371" data-end="381">controls</code> → кнопки (пуск, пауза, звук)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13lzi8t" data-start="413" data-end="459">
<p data-start="415" data-end="459"><code data-start="415" data-end="432">src="video.mp4"</code> → имя твоего видео файла</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="461" data-end="464">
<h1 data-section-id="hx8x4z" data-start="466" data-end="485">📌 КУДА ВСТАВЛЯТЬ</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="icrn7j" data-start="487" data-end="509">👉 В твой HTML файл</h2>
<p data-start="511" data-end="583">Открываешь файл <code data-start="527" data-end="539">index.html</code> и вставляешь <strong data-start="553" data-end="572">внутрь <code data-start="562" data-end="570">&lt;body&gt;</code></strong>, например:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="585" data-end="749"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Копировать" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Редактировать"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 